Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're prepared to die, then come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride... on a sea train!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoooa! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is Rocketman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even allow passengers to be on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it. I've finished servicing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water and coal have been loaded\Nand it's storing the steam right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were getting it ready for us, pops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait to rejoice until you survive the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this was a failure built\Nbefore Puffing Tom was completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you tune it up,\Nits steam engine can't control the speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thanks, Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... take us with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Bro, Franky, was taken\Nin by the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go after them... but we can't\Nget through Aqua Laguna by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to save Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.18,0:01:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're deeply indebted to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... pirates! \NDon't go getting thrown off, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now departing Water Seven for Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the sea train Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go...! \NTo get everything back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:39.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:46.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:49.60,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:04.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:11.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:18.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:26.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:37.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:48.12,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:55.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.34,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:11.48,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:29.99,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Rescue Our Friends! A Bond\NAmong Foes Sworn with Fists!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming out at a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an underground canal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got some water in my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gonna happen when you stand out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I didn't see that coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's getting fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey, monster granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't we falling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is real close now. \NWe'll keep on going and go down in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The sea train has come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Now we're gonna charge forth, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump! Sodom! Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping us,\Nthe entire Franky Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the connection cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those must be the highest-grade bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots! \NDon't be reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheerful bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, monster granny! \NIs this as fast as it goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fast at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it gets on the railway, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Railway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's drifted quite a ways away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've observed the sea train\N since its development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent message from the engine room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train will get on the railway shortly.\NOnce it does, it'll rapidly accelerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight to something so\Nthat your injuries won't be severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll get injured regardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! I missed it. \NBut I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Behave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! A little to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it next... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney! Gonbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and\Ncome inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're okay! We're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a sec, okay?\NI'll stop the train right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brake doesn't work on this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Hm? What the heck?\NThat kinda looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Straw Hat brother! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Hurry and get\NChimney and Gonbe inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get on the railway,\Nthey'll be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! All right! They got on the railway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Hey! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from Kokoro-san! \NShe's something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, I was afraid of\Nwhat was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, indeed. \NThat's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those high waves, it must've\Nbeen hard to find the railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, indeed.\N You're exactly righ... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, indeed, indeed. Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, she's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We definitely have to let Iceberg-san know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right. \NI-I'm sure he's worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, indeed. Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I bet he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about a guy who\Nsurvived being hit by a sea train...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know... that the violent\Ndisciple of Tom, Cutty Flam, died?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hit by the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first disciple of Tom,\Nthe world's greatest shipwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can do it... I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro-san, let's drink\Ntogether one of these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when we have something to drink to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san... please just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect... everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town... and these blueprints as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(447,447)}"Four years later"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you'd know who if I tell you "Cutty Flam."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.51,0:13:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show him in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turn him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a roundabout way of meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... anyway, what's up with\Nthat funny looking body of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Since my whole\Nbody came to be of no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rebuilt my body using \Niron scraps and escaped death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that your company contracts to\Nbuild ships for the World Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna tolerate you doing\Nthings that help the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took Tom-san and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who made the weapons\Nthat caused the incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have things you wanna say to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't think that I've forgiven\Nyou in the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you had the nerve\Nto show your face after what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely thought that you were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since the Government told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Tom-san forgave you,\NI'm not going to forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What the hell are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these the blueprints we\Nsaw for that ancient weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use the name Cutty Flam from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government couldn't\Nget this out of Tom-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time before I get targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the island with them... Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutty Flam from Tom's Workers is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't use that name,\Nthere'll be no connection between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, if you leave the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the blueprints' whereabouts\Nwill vanish into the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if they come after you\Nwhen you don't have them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said what I came to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, Iceberg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may not see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to end up like Tom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the blueprints with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, by any chance, you find that your\Nlife is in danger, just hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna do that, then you\Ncan even burn them before their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were me, would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san achieved so many great things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he gave up everything in order to\Npreserve these blueprints for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, as long as there's a risk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a woman named Nico Robin\Ncan restore the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the world needs those blueprints to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue to keep them with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I am to be killed...\NI won't give them to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may build this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't my giving them\Nto you answer that question?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet face to face,\Nwe yell at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't forgive you... and you\Nmay feel the same about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky... I'm... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...glad that... you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stupid-berg! \NI'm not gonna leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I wanna do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never do what you \Ntell me to, even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:16:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Moron-ky! Why don't\Nyou get what I'm saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is in order to protect the blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's you who's not getting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna leave no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Why am I remembering\Nhim at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that idiot... Iceberg... doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, obviously! \NGeez, I told you, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you'd get blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that acceleration sure was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Geez...\N--Yeah, really, that scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my lower back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are weird guys in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to go with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I tried\Nto stop you, you didn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy you'd go this far\Nto rescue your friend from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is also the culprit who tried to kill Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, there are lots of\Nthings that I wanna say to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie! We're not gonna\Nlet you steal all the glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that we'd be able to find\NIceberg-san's assassins if we followed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we hid in the tender together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... it seems we were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us join you guys in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the foes you're gonna get revenge\Non took Big Bro Franky as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! And we clearly know who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna take responsibility \Nif something happens to Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's Iceberg-san\Nwho's endured the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys going on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie! First, explain it to us! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Paulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the true culprit, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not that dense.\N We have a rough idea as to who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could guess if they\Nsuddenly disappeared for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll tell you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true identities of those masked men are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Lucci, Kaku, Kalifa and Blueno from the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was them who tried to kill Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You never even guessed that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But you said they went\Nback to their hometowns!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they, during an emergency like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it was Michael and\NHoichael from the backstreets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You don't know them?!\NThey're famous in the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!\NTo start with, you guys are--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Boy, I ate a lot.\N I'm finally full.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we got in fights back in\Ntown with both the Franky Family
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Galley-La shipwrights,\Nwe're all going after the same enemy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest one among the guys\Nwe're gonna fight is that pigeon guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mine. I'm definitely gonna beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is a battle to get back\Nwhat those four took from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, if we don't\Nreach them, nothing will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Grandma! Grandma! \NIt's Aqua Laguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? It's already here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney! Let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro-san! Is it okay for you to leave\Nthe engine room at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We somehow need to dodge that high wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?\NThat we can't control Rocketman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we want to operate it,\Nnothing works, including the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job ended when the train got on the railway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, the train is always\Nrunning at full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do anything, the train will\Ncrash into the big wave! Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we have the same goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's senseless to fight separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. We're comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends are also in\Nthe train that left before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fighting force will still increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Don't let that big wave beat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all achieve our goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:33.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:38.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:47.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:56.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You're braver and more caring than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:23:06.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:15.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! That wave is really huge! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! If we don't do something,\Nit'll collide with Rocketman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's do it, shall we, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--What're you guys gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fire a cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Smash the Wave! Luffy and Zoro\NUse the Strongest Combo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
